com.ibm.zrl.idmx.key
Class IssuerPublicKey

java.lang.Object
  com.ibm.zrl.idmx.key.IssuerPublicKey

public final class IssuerPublicKey
extends java.lang.Object

The Issuer's public key for the CL-signature scheme. In addition to the key itself, this object also contains the epochLength (which defines intervals when credentials expire), and a unique identifier to identify the key.

See Also:
IssuerPrivateKey, IssuerKeyPair

computeCurrentEpoch

public java.math.BigInteger computeCurrentEpoch()
Returns:
Current epoch. Computes an integer value representing the current epoch. The current epoch is computed as floor( currentTime/epochLength), where the currentTime and epochLength are in seconds.
